---
const props = Astro.props;

import ImageCard from '../../ImageCard.astro';
import icon from '../../../assets/inventory/staff/Life Fondness.png'
---

<ImageCard image={icon} title="Life Fondness">
<p>When casting a single-target [Support] skill on allies, grants <span class="text-orange-500">1</span> random [<span class="text-yellow-500">Level 1 Buff</span>]-[<span class="text-yellow-500">Level 2 Buff</span>] for <span class="text-orange-500">2</span>-<span class="text-orange-500">3</span> turns. If the target is a [summoned character], additionally grants [<span class="text-blue-500">Life Fondness I</span>]-[<span class="text-blue-500">Life Fondness II</span>] for <span class="text-orange-500">2</span>-<span class="text-orange-500">3</span> turns; can inflict [Life Fondness] up to <span class="text-orange-500">1</span> time every <span class="text-orange-500">3</span>-<span class="text-orange-500">1</span> turns.</p>
</ImageCard>
